All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
GameWindow
This class implements the gameWindow GUI, this is used for the game itself.
Island
This class implements an Island that can be travelled to, this island has its own store an posible routes to get here from other islands.
Item
This class implements an Item which can be bought and sold at the other islands in exchange for money.
Main
This class implements Main which creates the items, stores and islands.
MainMenu
This class implements the mainMenu GUI, this GUI is used to set up some of the game paramiters such as ship name, how many day the game will run for and what ship the player wants to use.
Route
This class implements a Route which specifies the route from one island to another.
Ship
This class implements a Ship which contains the traders bought items and can have have more capacity and travel faster depending on the ship created.
ShipUpgradeCannon
This class implements a Item which is a cannon, the item allows the trader to have a higher chance of wining a battle against the pirates.
Store
This class implements a Store which specifies the items that can be bought and sold by the trader.
Trader
This class implements a Trader which specifies the amount of money the trader has as well as what ship they have.
